snippet.title: Pokémon: Towering Legends
snippet.description:
Here we are, a Pokémon flash game! This is a matching game where you have to stack crystals into towers and earn the highest points. It's weird 'cause the only thing related to Pokémon here is the anime and the typing emblems.

This game is available on BlueMaxima's Flashpoint:
https://bluemaxima.org/flashpoint/

Become a Mudkip Recruit! https://tinyurl.com/mudkipshades

#MudkipWithShades #FlashGame #Pokemon #PokemonToweringLegends
